task.summary: Default task
Replaced some qualifiers with import.
Email user an unlock key every time s/he tries to login
Added throws tag
Fixed storing result
Improved Emailer
Close mysql connection when Model destruct.
Fixed Newick format
Increase svg frame size
Implement Guest user
Don't dump mysql database if no argument supplied.
ProjectConfig::setConfig doesn't require a title to exist. If a title/key is not found, it'll be added. If already exists, it'll be updated.
Added CPU, RAM usage and exec time for AW and DM
Add extra (unintended) messages to debug.log for debugging purposes.
Update readme to clarify the input limitations
Add instructions on how to install GNU time
Switched to *nix unzip as PHP's ZipArchive is unreliable.
Fixed uploading FASTA files as it was accidentally removed in a previous commit
Checking sequence now uses count_chars instead of preg_match_all as it has problems with memory allocation.
Added a new sample dataset
Filter hyphens in uploaded sequences
Replaced DateTime qualifier with an import
Replace ? with URL_SEPARATOR
